parameters.messageText: When I arrived, a bulky dude was waiting at the gates.

parameters.name: Bulky Dude
parameters.messageText: "Hey! You must be the new guy!"

parameters.name: Keisuke
parameters.messageText: "I am Urayame Keisuke! You can call me Kei-kun."
He extends his hand to me, as if he knew me forever.
